      "content": "that's a really dark way to put it. but i guess it feels true. i look in the mirror and i don't even recognize myself. i'm just going through the motions... wake up, eat, sleep, repeat. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but nothing ever does. it's just exhausting.",
